originalText.text: Completely unprofessional. This woman was a no-show at her own office -she did no cancel our appointment and has yet to return any of my calls to at least explain what happened. We still waited in the lobby over 30 minutes and I left 3 voicemails -still, nothing. How inconsiderate and insensitive. I'm going to make sure to report this to my insurance so they drop her.
